            <category>Swift</category>
            <category>collection</category>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Claude Code 免费模型接入使用说明]]></title>
            <link>https://mikeq95.github.io/blog/2026/04/29/free-claude-code</link>
            <guid>https://mikeq95.github.io/blog/2026/04/29/free-claude-code</guid>
            <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[快速启动（两步完成）]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="快速启动两步完成">快速启动（两步完成）<a href="https://mikeq95.github.io/blog/2026/04/29/free-claude-code#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E4%B8%A4%E6%AD%A5%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90" class="hash-link" aria-label="快速启动（两步完成）的直接链接" title="快速启动（两步完成）的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="第一步启动服务器终端-1">第一步：启动服务器（终端 1）<a href="https://mikeq95.github.io/blog/2026/04/29/free-claude-code#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF-1" class="hash-link" aria-label="第一步：启动服务器（终端 1）的直接链接" title="第一步：启动服务器（终端 1）的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">cd free-claude-code</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">uv run uvicorn server:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8082</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<blockquote>
<p>✅ <strong>成功标志：</strong> 看到 <code>Uvicorn running on http://0.0.0.0:8082</code> 提示 ⚠️ <strong>注意：</strong> 不要关闭此窗口，必须保持运行状态</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="第二步启动-claude-code终端-2">第二步：启动 Claude Code（终端 2）<a href="https://mikeq95.github.io/blog/2026/04/29/free-claude-code#%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8-claude-code%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF-2" class="hash-link" aria-label="第二步：启动 Claude Code（终端 2）的直接链接" title="第二步：启动 Claude Code（终端 2）的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>新开一个终端窗口，运行：</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN="freecc" ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL="http://localhost:8082" claude</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="️-切换模型配置">⚙️ 切换模型配置<a href="https://mikeq95.github.io/blog/2026/04/29/free-claude-code#%EF%B8%8F-%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE" class="hash-link" aria-label="⚙️ 切换模型配置的直接链接" title="⚙️ 切换模型配置的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>根据需求修改 <code>.env</code> 文件来切换底层模型：</p>
<p><strong>切换为 Kimi K2</strong>（编程能力最强）</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">sed -i '' 's|MODEL="nvidia_nim/z-ai/glm4.7"|MODEL="nvidia_nim/moonshotai/kimi-k2-instruct"|' /Users/a1234/free-claude-code/.env</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>切换为 GLM-4.7</strong>（中文能力较强）</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">sed -i '' 's|MODEL="nvidia_nim/moonshotai/kimi-k2-instruct"|MODEL="nvidia_nim/z-ai/glm4.7"|' /Users/a1234/free-claude-code/.env</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>验证当前模型</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">grep MODEL /Users/a1234/free-claude-code/.env</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-应用更改">🔄 应用更改<a href="https://mikeq95.github.io/blog/2026/04/29/free-claude-code#-%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9" class="hash-link" aria-label="🔄 应用更改的直接链接" title="🔄 应用更改的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>修改模型后，需重启服务器才能生效：</p>
<ol>
<li class="">在终端 1 按 <code>Ctrl+C</code> 停止当前服务</li>
<li class="">重新运行启动命令：</li>
</ol>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">cd free-claude-code</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">uv run uvicorn server:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8082</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-注意事项">📝 注意事项<a href="https://mikeq95.github.io/blog/2026/04/29/free-claude-code#-%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9" class="hash-link" aria-label="📝 注意事项的直接链接" title="📝 注意事项的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<table><thead><tr><th>事项</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>🟢 保持运行</td><td>终端 1（服务器）必须一直开着，关闭后 Claude Code 将无法连接</td></tr><tr><td>💡 显示说明</td><td>底层使用 NVIDIA NIM 免费模型，界面显示 "Sonnet 4.6" 属正常现象</td></tr><tr><td>⏱️ 使用限额</td><td>免费额度限制为 <strong>40 次 / 分钟</strong></td></tr><tr><td>🔒 安全提醒</td><td>请勿将 API Key 泄露给他人</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content:encoded>
            <category>#claude</category>
